      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants quality without the 'brand new' price tag. Everything is running smoothly, and it's ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have! \u2728",
