    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a mid-engine masterpiece featuring the 3.4L M97 flat-six powerplant. This unit is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, offering an involving driving experience. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a low polar moment of inertia and a MacPherson strut suspension geometry that provides exceptional feedback. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc aluminum fixed calipers over cross-drilled rotors, ensuring consistent thermal management. Mechanically, the VarioCam Plus system provides seamless lift and timing transitions. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is robust, with a recently documented service including a cooling system refresh and a new set of N-spec tires. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
