    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in a sophisticated Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the Parchment leather interior remains supple and free of tears or odors; it has been a strictly smoke-free environment since day one. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium 12-speaker audio system and power liftgate, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this Lexus is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent synthetic oil change and a full brake inspection completed just last month. The Michelin tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a smooth, quiet ride for the next owner. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the V6 engine runs whisper-quiet. This listing includes two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand. This is a dependable, high-quality SUV ready for its next chapter.",
